title: Skins - Series Finale Soundtrack
description:
This is all the songs from the Skins season 2 finale (okay, not all, cause I left out Britney and couldn&#039;t found some songs, so I put another from the same band/singer). The series will be continue, but with a different cast, so that&#039;s way I named this as a series finale.
So, f*ck it and enjoy! ;)
